LJCDocDataFile.remarks:
The DocData XML is intended to contain the XML Comments based on the PHP
file structure of Classes, Methods and Properties.
<br />
<pre> &lt;LJCDocDataFile&gt;
	&lt;Name/&gt;
	&lt;Summary/&gt;
	&lt;Remarks/&gt;
	&lt;Classes&gt;
		&lt;Class&gt;
			&lt;Name/&gt;
			&lt;Summary/&gt;
			&lt;Remarks/&gt;
			&lt;Methods&gt;
				&lt;Method&gt;
					&lt;Name/&gt;
					&lt;Summary/&gt;
					&lt;Params&gt;
						&lt;Param&gt;
							&lt;Name/&gt;
							&lt;Summary/&gt;
						&lt;/Param&gt;
					&lt;/Params&gt;
					&lt;Remarks/&gt;
					&lt;Returns/&gt;
					&lt;Syntax/&gt;
					&lt;Code/&gt;
				&lt;/Method&gt;
			&lt;/Methods&gt;
			&lt;Properties&gt;
				&lt;Property&gt;
					&lt;Name/&gt;
					&lt;Summary/&gt;
					&lt;Syntax/&gt;
				&lt;/Property&gt;
			&lt;/Properties&gt;
		&lt;/Class&gt;
	&lt;/Classes&gt;
&lt;/LJCDocDataFile&gt;
